{"tid":941283,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"我研究真理之門多年 得出了這看法...","createTime":"2018-12-14T15:54:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T19:07:54.000Z","uid":150609,"like":21,"dislike":71,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"38e1c5a8d45a8a8abff696bedf1317d5cd2242f4","tid":941283,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:54:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HJGp5A9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHJGp5A9.jpg&h=c7e4b070&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「真理」曾經講過：<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">我就是稱為世界的存在，有人叫我做宇宙、有人叫我做神、有人叫我做真理，\n有人叫我做全，或者一；</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2vp7iYs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2vp7iYs.png&h=8c4d0e09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n愛德華被師父留在荒島訓練，愛德華在極度飢餓之際，竟然吃了螞蟻。近乎死後重生的經歷令他領悟到答案：<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">假如我沒有吃螞蟻，死後就會被螞蟻分解，然後螞蟻又會被其他動物吃掉&hellip;&hellip;這就是食物鏈。\n但不只是生物，這荒島幾萬年前出現，我們才可以在此&hellip;&hellip;萬事萬物都有關係，\n世界上的萬事萬物都在大循環之中。\n在這大循環之中，我與艾爾像螞蟻一樣只是小小的個體，只不過是「全」裡的一個「一」。\n但全靠有眾多微小的「一」，「全」才可以存在。</code></pre><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/14/232140_64d28fadb7e1fe9ed3a6e55e6e8f0d04.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F14%2F232140_64d28fadb7e1fe9ed3a6e55e6e8f0d04.png&h=bbfa9874&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n失去肢體的同時也得到了不用煉成陣就可以發動的能力。在打開那扇門的時候，得到的同時就意味著失去，失去的同時就意味著得到。<br />\n<br />\n只有不停留在後悔、怨恨當中的人（後悔是自己打開門，怨恨是被迫打開門），才能繼續向前，找到解開那邊界的鑰匙。<br />\n<br />\n每個人都有自己的真理之門，那就是一，就是全，自己就是真理本身。<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">我 即是你</code></pre><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ve6hGcD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fve6hGcD.png&h=8c0ea44e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總有一天會觸碰了各種禁忌的我們，只有懷抱著因失去而得到的東西，繼續向前，繼續向前&hellip;..<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xdhkD3s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxdhkD3s.png&h=c0c66749&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WieSu92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWieSu92.jpg&h=9aa9c95b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n生命之樹 十個質點 (10 Sephiroth)<br />\n生命之樹的十個質點是：<br />\n<br />\nⅠ Kether，王冠，Crown<br />\nⅡ Chochmah，智慧，Wisdom<br />\nⅢ Binah，理解，Understanding<br />\nⅣ Chesed，慈悲，Mercy<br />\nⅤ Geburah，嚴厲或力量，Severity / Fortitude<br />\nⅥ Tiphareth，美麗或平衡，Beauty / Balance<br />\nⅦ Netzach，勝利，Victory<br />\nⅧ Hod，宏偉，Splendour<br />\nⅨ Yesod，基礎，the Foundation<br />\nⅩ Malkuth，王國，the Kingdom<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">上 即係</span> 真理之門上既生命之樹<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">一即全  全即一 上即係生 </span>....<br />\n<br />\n而生命之樹下 是10個質點<br />\n<br />\n你已經睇到答案了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6AgtNY5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6AgtNY5.jpg&h=e72fca25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5iuZUDV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5iuZUDV.png&h=e7c2d0ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">一即全  全即一 上即係生 ーーー</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&quot; 下即係點 ＝＝&quot;</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cU6BcsC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcU6BcsC.png&h=ede624f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3347a2d0062d2440af0b614e6b96a1c26ab9b39e","tid":941283,"uid":35667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:55:14.000Z","msg":"做忌"},{"pid":"92547de9f6b3e1a50b0353e245611203b335004a","tid":941283,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3347a2d0062d2440af0b614e6b96a1c26ab9b39e","tid":941283,"uid":35667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:55:14.000Z","msg":"做忌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:56:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https: