ode></pre><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ve6hGcD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fve6hGcD.png&h=8c0ea44e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總有一天會觸碰了各種禁忌的我們，只有懷抱著因失去而得到的東西，繼續向前，繼續向前&hellip;..<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xdhkD3s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxdhkD3s.png&h=c0c66749&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WieSu92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWieSu92.jpg&h=9aa9c95b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n生命之樹 十個質點 (10 Sephiroth)<br />\n生命之樹的十個質點是：<br />\n<br />\nⅠ Kether，王冠，Crown<br />\nⅡ Chochmah，智慧，Wisdom<br />\nⅢ Binah，理解，Understanding<br />\nⅣ Chesed，慈悲，Mercy<br />\nⅤ Geburah，嚴厲或力量，Severity / Fortitude<br />\nⅥ Tiphareth，美麗或平衡，Beauty / Balance<br />\nⅦ Netzach，勝利，Victory<br />\nⅧ Hod，宏偉，Splendour<br />\nⅨ Yesod，基礎，the Foundation<br />\nⅩ Malkuth，王國，the Kingdom<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">上 即係</span> 真理之門上既生命之樹<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">一即全  全即一 上即係生 </span>....<br />\n<br />\n而生命之樹下 是10個質點<br />\n<br />\n你已經睇到答案了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6AgtNY5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6AgtNY5.jpg&h=e72fca25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5iuZUDV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5iuZUDV.png&h=e7c2d0ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">一即全  全即一 上即係生 ーーー</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&quot; 下即係點 ＝＝&quot;</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cU6BcsC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcU6BcsC.png&h=ede624f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T16:00:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T16:01:04.000Z","msg":"即係 下姐係點= = 囉"},{"pid":"23505aac83ec86157510f9175b2291e1f2f